==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mutessarif
<hw>Mu*tes`sa*rif"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Turk. & Ar.
<ets>mute⟦cced⟧arif</ets> freely disposing of anything, master.]</ety>
<def>In Turkey prior to the revolution, an administrative authority of
any of certain sanjaks. They were appointed directly by the
Sultan.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mutessarifat</ent>⟦br⟧
